comments: Hield (SAC) places his right hand momentarily on Monk's (LAL) front before removing it, and marginal contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal pivot foot as he releases the ball to start his dribble simultaneously with lifting his pivot.
Reaves (LAL) applies a stayed hand to Hield's (SAC) back, and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Hield (SAC) applies a left forearm momentarily to James' (LAL) right arm, and marginal contact occurs as James swings the ball from left to right on the driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) and Reaves (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during the screen, and marginal contact occurs.
James (LAL) plants his left leg to establish himself in a screening position in the path of Fox (SAC), and he absorbs the oncoming body contact to his backside.
Metu (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reaves (LAL) and firms up to absorb the oncoming contact.
James (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fox (SAC) and firms up to absorb the oncoming contact to his backside.
James (LAL) does not move through Fox's (SAC) space or otherwise extend into Fox to dislodge him from his defensive position and the contact is marginal.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Hield (SAC) slips and falls to the floor after receiving the pass and maintains a dribble before signaling for a timeout.
Monk (LAL) commits a take foul on Haliburton (SAC).
